</h3><p class="sc-edLa-Dd hZPWCc pf-51_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span>Guidelines from the Health and Safety Executive advise on handling penetrating wounds in children:



